Check if a FANC root id is up to date

Source: R/ids.R
fanc_islatest.Rd

Check if a FANC root id is up to date

Usage

fanc_islatest(x, timestamp = NULL, ...)

Arguments

x

FlyWire rootids in any format understandable to ngl_segments including as integer64

timestamp

(optional) argument to set an endpoint - edits after this time will be ignored (see details).

...

Additional arguments passed to flywire_islatest

See also

Other fanc-ids: fanc_cellid_from_segid(), fanc_ids(), fanc_latestid(), fanc_leaves(), fanc_rootid(), fanc_xyz2id()

Examples

fanc_islatest("648518346473954669")
#> [1] FALSE
